# iTerm2 Shell Integration
# Official iTerm2 shell integration for full APS (Automatic Profile Switching) support
#
# Features enabled:
# - Automatic Profile Switching (username, hostname, path, job matching)
# - Shell marks (navigate to previous prompts with Cmd-Shift-Up/Down)
# - Command history tracking
# - Directory tracking
# - Alert on command completion
# - Download/upload with scp
#
# Documentation: https://iterm2.com/documentation-shell-integration.html
#
# Last updated: 2025-11-24
#
# NOTE: Currently configured for regular iTerm2 sessions (non-tmux)
# Tmux integration will be configured separately once basic APS is working

# Source the official iTerm2 shell integration
# The integration script checks for iTerm2 and interactive mode
if test -f ~/.iterm2_shell_integration.fish
    source ~/.iterm2_shell_integration.fish
end
